data.description: Enter into this remarkable move-in ready end unit and feel right at home! Marvel at the soaring ceilings, calming neutral paint tones, and the bright inviting eat-in kitchen featuring rich cabinetry and stainless steel appliances! The oversized bedrooms, each with its own adjoining bath, along with a hall den, provide ample functional space for all your needs. Outside, enjoy the relaxation areas, including a balcony and deck offering tranquil panoramic views. The the two-car tandem garage ensures plenty of storage space. Don't miss out on this opportunity! Schedule a showing today! No HOA fees!
